Turkish Business Group Calls for Fiscal Rule to Control Budget

-- B y   A l i   B e r a t   M e r i c
-- 
2011-10-05T07:52:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/turkish-business-group-calls-for-fiscal-rule-to-control-budget.html
Turkey  needs a fiscal rule that
regulates budget spending and the debt load, Umit Boyner, head
of the Turkish Industrialists and Businessmen’s Association, the
country’s biggest business group, said in a televised speech
from Istanbul today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
